text: Ancus may refer to: * Ancus (genus), a genus of beetle in the family Carabidae * Ancus Marcius (7th century BC), king of Rome * 14088 Ancus, an asteroid * Ancus, an Italic praenomen * a part of a male Lepidoptera genitalia ==See also== * Ankus, a tool employed in the handling and training of elephants
title: Ancus
